            . I am a watchmaker, and have known May about eight years; I never heard a bad character of him before this; <rs id="t17640607-5-deflabel36" type="occupation">he workedin the watch way</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17640607-5-defend69 t17640607-5-deflabel36"></join>.</p>
