                  </persName>
            . I live at Walworth, in Surry, and am a watch-movement-maker. May served his time with my son: he works in the steel-work part. I never knew but he was a very honest diligent man: he has worked for me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17640607-5-person82">
                  Charles 
                  Thompson 
               <interp inst="t17640607-5-person82" type="surname" value="Thompson"></interp>
