                     <interp inst="t17640607-5-person82" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . May served his time with me, and has been out of his time two years; I never knew any thing amiss of him, or heard any thing bad of him in my life. I have seen Stanley about Newington; <rs id="t17640607-5-deflabel37" type="occupation">he worked at tinkering, and sometimes goes with a barrow, grinding of knives</rs>
